OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FItaly leaves children of   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsame-sex parents in limbo  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, In 2018, Maria Silvia Fiengo and       
OL,6, Francesca Pardi were among Italy's     
OL,7, first same-sex couples to be registered
OL,8, as parents.                            
OL,10,FThe mayor of Milan, Giuseppe Sala, took
OL,11,Fa progressive stance and allowed       
OL,12,Fchildren born to parents of the same   
OL,13,Fgender to be acknowledged in the       
OL,14,Fabsence of clear national legislation. 
OL,16,FFor Maria Silvia and Francesca - and   
OL,17,Ftheir four children Margherita, twins  
OL,18,FGiorgio and Raffaele, and Antonio -    
OL,19,Fbeing finally recognised as a household
OL,20,Fafter years of legal challenges and    
OL,21,Fdiscrimination was "truly incredible". 
